name: Twinkle Toes
description:
This is a print from an original oil painting by Linda Boucher.

Sparkly ruby heels, perfect for the boudoir, dressing room or your dream of a shoe room.
Just click your heels... and away you go!

This is 8"x10" printed on Ilford Gallerie Smooth GlossPaper 290g/m, using archival inks.

It is unframed and unmatted, and will be sent with a protective cellophane sleeve, in a cardboard strengthened envelope.

Copyright for this Image belongs solely to Linda Boucher, and is not transfered with sale of item. Use of it without express permission is horrible and prohibited... and will give you bunions.
